{{Vgname|雷顿教授与魔神之笛|ja=レイトン教授と魔神の笛|na=Professor Layton and the Last Specter|eu=Professor Layton and the Spectre's Call}}是由[[Level-5|Level-5]]开发于掌上游戏机[[任天堂DS|任天堂DS]]平台的[[益智游戏|益智]][[冒险游戏|冒险]][[电子游戏|电子游戏]]。《魔神之笛》是[[雷顿教授系列|雷顿教授系列]]的第四作，游戏剧情发生于系列首作《[[雷頓教授與不可思議城鎮|不可思议城镇]]》的三年前，游戏讲述了雷顿教授和他的学生路克·特莱顿相遇的故事。游戏一共包含170个谜题。

《雷顿教授与魔神之笛》中附带了一个名为《雷顿教授的伦敦生活》的[[電子角色扮演遊戲|角色扮演游戏]]，其可以从游戏的载入屏幕中进入。在《伦敦生活》中，玩家将操控角色，在一个叫“小伦敦”的小镇中和其他角色互动，广告称游戏可玩超过100小时。欧版为避免因翻译而导致发行过晚，故取消了《伦敦生活》这一功能。

游戏于2009年在日本发售，并在发售首周排到了是周游戏销售榜首位。2011年发行的美版和PAL区版也受到了广泛好评，游戏在[[GameRankings|GameRankings]]和[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]中分别的到了84%和83分。

== 系统 ==

《雷顿教授与魔神之笛》是一个以冒险形式托出谜题的游戏。在游戏中，玩家将操作一行三人——教授艾尔夏尔·雷顿、助手蕾米·阿尔塔瓦和少年男孩路克·特莱顿——在一个叫霧谷的小镇移动。随着剧情的发展，他们三人需要在村庄中不断解决谜题。虽然雾谷被分成了很多部分，但很多地方需在在情节发展到一定程度才能访问。玩家若要在雾谷中移动，则需点击触摸屏右下角的鞋形图标，然后根据箭头的指示来选择行进的方向<ref name="lsmanualp11">{{cite manual | title = Professor Layton and the Last Specter Instruction Booklet| section = Exploring| publisher = Nintendo of America| date = 2011-10-17| accessdate =2011-10-22 | quote = First, tap the shoe icon. Then tap an arrow or a hand icon to move.|page = 11}}</ref>。在雾谷中，玩家可以点击任天堂DS下屏的任何地方，并以此来调查对象，显示对白，寻找提示硬币、收藏品或隐藏谜题<ref name="ignreviewls">{{cite web|url=http://ds.ign.com/articles/120/1200890p1.html|title=Professor Layton and the Last Specter Review|accessdate=2011-10-17|publisher=IGN|year=2011|author=Drake, Audrey|archive-date=2011-10-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111019012348/http://ds.ign.com/articles/120/1200890p1.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。同样的，如果屏幕上有非玩家角色，玩家还可以通过点击它们发起对话<ref name="lsmanualp12">{{cite manual | title = Professor Layton and the Last Specter Instruction Booklet| section = Talking to People| publisher = Nintendo of America| date = 2011-10-17| accessdate =2011-10-22 | quote = Tap a character on the Touch Screen to interact with him/her.|page = 12}}</ref>。

=== 谜题 ===

在游戏对话中或是主界面调查时，系统通常会要求玩家解决一个谜题<ref name="lsmanualp13b">{{cite manual | title = Professor Layton and the Last Specter Instruction Booklet| section = Solving Puzzles| publisher = Nintendo of America| date = 2011-10-17| accessdate =2011-10-22 | quote = It will be important to solve as many puzzles as possible in order to progress through the story! Talk to people and search the surrounding area for puzzles.|page = 13}}</ref>。而因剧情进展而错过的谜题则都会交给一只叫基特的猫，该角色可以将问题存起来，留之以后解决<ref name="noegameplay" />。游戏中有超过170个谜题<ref name="noewhatsnew">{{Cite web |url=http://www.nintendo.co.uk/NOE/en_GB/games/ms/plsc/whatsnew.html |title=Professor Layton and the Spectre's Call – What's New |accessdate=2011-11-12 |publisher=Nintendo of Europe |year=2011 |work=Professor Layton and the Spectre's Call – Official Website |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/639JCjpHl?url=http://www.nintendo.co.uk/NOE/en_GB/games/ms/plsc/whatsnew.html |archivedate=2011-11-12 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>，其中包括[[脑筋急转弯|脑筋急转弯]]、[[滑动解谜|滑动解谜]]、[[逻辑解谜|逻辑解谜]]、[[孔明棋|孔明棋]]等多种类型。在一个谜题开始时，游戏将首先告诉玩家谜题的名称、编号及该题的“灵光点数”，而玩家也可以通过点数系统估计谜题的难度<ref name="noegameplay" />。在剧情游戏模式中，玩家不会用到灵光点，但当灵光点达到一定数值时，玩家就可从游戏载入菜单中进入附加关卡<ref name="noegameplay" />。

在谜题第一屏过去后，屏幕将显示谜题主界面，玩家需要通过触摸屏操作，并依据DS上屏给出的要求来解决谜题。每个谜题的解决时间都无限制，同时游戏内置的[[笔记本|笔记]]功能还可以协助解决谜题。如果玩家暂不想解决一个谜题，则可点击屏幕上的退出按钮，退出操作不会影响灵光点数<ref name="noegameplay" />。此外，每个谜题都有三个提示，每层提示都可以使用一枚“提示硬币”解锁，如果玩家仍然需要更多的提示，则也可以解开第四个“S提示”，此提示更为详细，但需要耗费两枚提示硬币<ref name="noeparents" /><ref name="lsmanualp14a">{{cite manual | title = Professor Layton and the Last Specter Instruction Booklet| section = Solving Puzzles| publisher = Nintendo of America| date = 2011-10-17| accessdate =2011-10-22 | quote = There are four hints for each puzzle. The first three hints cost one coin each, but the Super Hint costs two hint coins. There are a limited number of hint coins in the game, so use them sparingly!|page = 14}}</ref>。然而，提示硬币的数量有限，游戏会建议玩家把硬币用在刀刃上<ref name="lsmanualp14a" />。玩家初始时有10枚提示硬币，而之后则可以通过调查村庄各个角落而获得<ref name="lsgameprorev">{{cite web |url=http://www.gamepro.com/article/reviews/224025/review-professor-layton-and-the-last-specter-ds/ |title=Review: Professor Layton and the Last Specter (DS) |accessdate=2011-10-18 |publisher=GamePro |year=2011 |author=Haywald, Justin |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/63bHeQpza?url=http://www.gamepro.com/article/reviews/224025/review-professor-layton-and-the-last-specter-ds/ |archivedate=2011-12-01 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。

玩家需要通过在DS下屏给出答案来解开谜题。有的谜题需要玩家在点击“解答”选项后，通过输入字符或数字来作答。还有的谜题则需要在屏幕上画圈，或是点击屏幕某区域后，再点击“确定”提交答案。另有一些则会在玩家正确找到解决方案时自动解决<ref name="lsmanualp14b">{{cite manual | title = Professor Layton and the Last Specter Instruction Booklet| section = Solving Puzzles| publisher = Nintendo of America| date = 2011-10-17| accessdate =2011-10-22 | quote = Some puzzles will end automatically when you've arrived at the right answer, and others require you to submit your answer manually.|page = 14}}</ref>。如果玩家在解谜过程中已发现犯错，则可通过点击“重试”按钮重解谜题。重试谜题不会归还已扣除的灵光点和提示硬币<ref name="ignreviewls" />。若玩家提交的回答不正确，系统将会要求玩家重做谜题，同时根据谜题的答案选项数扣除一定的灵光点<ref name="ignreviewls" />。若玩家做出了正确的回答，系统将会奖励题目所值的灵光点<ref name="noegameplay" />，同时剧情也会继续进行<ref name="lsmanualp13b" />。游戏设有谜题词典功能，其列出了玩家完成的全部谜题，玩家可以随时工具箱菜单中进入谜题词典，并可重做这些谜题<ref name="noegameplay">{{Cite web |url=http://www.nintendo.co.uk/NOE/en_GB/games/ms/plsc/gameplay.html |title=Professor Layton and the Spectre's Call – Gameplay |accessdate=2011-11-12 |publisher=Nintendo of Europe |year=2011 |work=Professor Layton and the Spectre's Call – Official Website |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/639IK3xFH?url=http://www.nintendo.co.uk/NOE/en_GB/games/ms/plsc/gameplay.html |archivedate=2011-11-12 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。完成有些谜题后，玩家可以获得小道具，他们可以在[[迷你游戏|迷你游戏]]中使用。

玩家亦可通过[[Nintendo_Wi-Fi_Connection|Nintendo Wi-Fi Connection]]下载额外的“周刊谜题通信”，该功能可从游戏载入菜单访问<ref name="noegameplay" />。这些谜题的提示不能通过提示硬币购买，但可以在迷题发布一周后免费获得<ref name="lsmanualp25">{{cite manual | title = Professor Layton and the Last Specter Instruction Booklet| section = Weekly Nintendo Wi-Fi Connection Puzzles| publisher = Nintendo of America| date = 2011-10-17| accessdate =2011-10-22 | quote = When available, hints will be provided for downloaded puzzles one week after their release. The first time you connect and download puzzles from Nintendo WFC, all currently available puzzles and hints will be downloaded.|page = 25}}</ref>。当玩家连接到Wi-Fi Connection时即可下载当前的所有谜题和提示<ref name="lsmanualp25" />。

=== 小游戏 ===

在《雷顿教授与魔神之笛》中剧情模式中设有几个小游戏，它们玩家可以通过点击小镇移动界面右上角的教授手提箱载入。这些小游戏在剧情的发展到一定程度时才能解锁，同时玩家还需要通过解决游戏中困难的谜题来获得小游戏要素<ref name="eurogamerlsrev">{{cite web|url=http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2011-10-21-professor-layton-and-the-last-specter-review|title=Professor Layton and the Last Specter – Review|accessdate=2011-10-21|publisher=EuroGamer|year=2011|author=Teti, John|archive-date=2011-10-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111022130013/http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2011-10-21-professor-layton-and-the-last-specter-review|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

在小游戏“玩具火车”中，玩家需要在游戏板中铺设复杂的[[铁轨|铁轨]]。在游戏中，玩具火车必须要通过各个火车站并到达终点，在更高难度的关卡中，玩家还必须控制时间使其避开汽车和其他列车<ref name="wiredmajinnofue">{{Cite news|url=http://www.wired.com/gamelife/2009/11/professor-layton/|title=What's New in Professor Layton's Fourth Outing|accessdate=2011-11-11|publisher=Wired|author=Kohler, Chris|work=GameLife|date=2009-11-30|archive-date=2011-10-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111031101130/http://www.wired.com/gamelife/2009/11/professor-layton/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。玩具火车的移动需要[[燃料|燃料]]，若不能在到达终点前收集到更多燃料，则玩家必须控制轨道的长度<ref name="wiredmajinnofue" />。

在小游戏“鱼”中，玩家将要控制一条鱼来收集水箱里的全部金币。在游戏中鱼将沿着直斜线移动，同时玩家可通过在特定位置防止气泡，使鱼的路径在不同的方向[[反射|反射]]<ref name="noewhatsnew" />。在日版游戏中，玩家需要按一定法则变换文字，并通过匹配出特定单词来喂养鱼<ref name="wiredmajinnofue" />。

在小游戏“人偶剧”中，玩家需要将当前剧本顺利编排下去<ref name="wiredmajinnofue" />。如果玩家选择的词语在剧目中讲不通，则此剧就会直接结束，游戏会要求玩家重新尝试；如果所有的选择都正确，则可看到此剧的后记并受到观众的赞扬。

当剧情发展到足够程度后，玩家用在雾谷点击街道上老鼠得到的“老鼠徽章”来进入另一个游戏“打地鼠”<ref name="noewhatsnew" /><ref name="grevreview">{{cite web|url=http://www.gamerevolution.com/review/professor-layton-and-the-last-spectre|title=Professor Layton and the Last Specter Review|accessdate=2011-10-11|publisher=GameRevolution|year=2011|author=Tan, Nick|archive-date=2014-09-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140918042933/http://www.gamerevolution.com/review/professor-layton-and-the-last-spectre|dead-url=no}}</ref>。与其他的小游戏不同，该游戏需要和雾谷中一角色对话后进入，而非手提箱。游戏的目标是在有限时间内砸中更多的老鼠，同时避免误伤路克的老鼠托比。这也是游戏中唯一的即时性元素。

=== 雷顿教授的伦敦生活 ===
{{vgname-nb|雷顿教授的伦敦生活|ja=レイトン教授のロンドンライフ|en=Professor Layton's London Life}}是由[[Level-5|Level-5]]与[[Brownie_Brown|Brownie Brown]]合作开发的角色扮演游戏，游戏内植于《雷顿教授与魔神之笛》中<ref name="ascomb1i">{{cite web |url=http://andriasang.com/comb1i/ |title=Professor Layton Gets a 100 Hour RPG |accessdate=2011-11-05 |publisher=Andriasang |year=2011 |author=Gantayat, Anoop |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20130102003825/http://andriasang.com/comb1i/layton_london_life/ |archivedate=2013-01-02 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。在《伦敦生活》中，玩家需要创建一个[[纸娃娃系统|角色]]并定制其着装与配饰。玩家控制的角色生活于一个灵感来自[[伦敦|伦敦]]的城市——“小伦敦”中<ref name="l5iapr" />。在小伦敦，玩家可以建造并装饰自己的房间，同时为小伦敦的居民跑腿办事，而这些居民多又取自当时雷顿系列全四部游戏中的角色。此外游戏还包括当年晚些时候发布的动画电影《[[雷顿教授与永远的歌姬|雷顿教授与永远的歌姬]]》中的角色，如歌剧演员珍妮丝、梅丽娜和奥斯瓦尔德<ref name="laytonjpll">{{cite web|url=http://www.layton.jp/majin/london.html|title=レイトン教授のロンドンライフ 秘密のパスワードを公開！|accessdate=2011-10-11|publisher=Level-5 Inc.|year=2009|work=layton.jp|language=ja|archive-date=2011-10-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111027070104/http://www.layton.jp/majin/london.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。玩家帮助居民后会得到可以用来进入城市新领域道具或家具，还能获得财富与幸福<ref name="l5iapr" /><ref name="ascomb1i" />。玩家可以使用Nintendo Wi-Fi Connection连接到互联网并上传角色，同时还可通过[[friend_code|friend code]]与其他玩家交易<ref name="lsmanualp37">{{cite manual | title = Professor Layton and the Last Specter Instruction Booklet| section = Fun With Wireless Communications| publisher = Nintendo of America| date = 2011-10-17| accessdate =2011-11-06| quote = After you've progressed far enough in the game, you and a friend can create visiting versions of your own characters in each other's towns via Nintendo Wi-Fi Connection.|page = 37}}</ref>。官方宣称《伦敦生活》有至少100个小时的游戏时间<ref name="ascomb1i" />。当一台任天堂DS与另一台[[睡眠状态|睡眠状态]]下运行同一游戏任天堂DS无线连接时，玩家可通过任天堂DS的Tag mode可以与他人进行游戏物品交易<ref name="wiredmajinnofue" />。

《雷顿教授的伦敦生活》的名称源于Level-5在2012年首发的游戏《[[幻想生活|幻想生活]]》<ref name="ascomb1i" /><ref name="ascomyl0">{{cite web |url=http://andriasang.com/comyl0/ |title=Level-5 Vision 2011 Live Blog |accessdate=2011-11-05 |publisher=Andriasang |year=2011 |author=Gantayat, Anoop |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20130102022844/http://andriasang.com/comyl0/ |archivedate=2013-01-02 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。在日版中，《伦敦生活》只能在完成《魔神之笛》主游戏后才能进行<ref name="ascomb1i" />，而美版<ref name="noaexclusive">{{Cite web |url=http://www.nintendo.com/whatsnew/detail/qTLe9wQB7Gec6xW-E6Uc7-vK7rVsmUDt |title=The Legend of Zelda: Skyward Sword Bundle Highlights a Golden Autumn for Nintendo Games |accessdate=2011-11-12 |publisher=Nintendo of America |year=2011 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/639aJq8g0?url=http://www.nintendo.com/whatsnew/detail/qTLe9wQB7Gec6xW-E6Uc7-vK7rVsmUDt |archivedate=2011-11-13 |deadurl=no }}</ref>和澳版<ref name="nwrausll">{{cite web|url=http://www.nintendoworldreport.com/news/28079|title=Australian Layton Release to Include London Life|accessdate=2011-11-05|publisher=Nintendo World Report|year=2011|author=Bray, Nicholas|archive-date=2012-03-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120331022223/http://www.nintendoworldreport.com/news/28079|dead-url=no}}</ref>则在游戏开始时就可访问。由于翻译需要大量的时间，而欧版为了在2011年内正常发售，故未在游戏中加入《伦敦生活》这一部分<ref name="onmlondonlifeuk">{{cite web|url=http://www.officialnintendomagazine.co.uk/29935/professor-laytons-london-life-is-coming-to-europe/ |title=Professor Layton's London Life isn't coming to Europe |accessdate=2011-11-03 |publisher=Future Publishing Ltd. |year=2011 |author=East, Thomas |work=Official Nintendo Magazine |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20111019183931/http://www.officialnintendomagazine.co.uk/29935/professor-laytons-london-life-is-coming-to-europe/ |archivedate=2011-10-19 }}</ref><ref name="inferioreu">{{cite web|url=http://www.cubed3.com/news/16056|title=Nintendo Confirms Inferior EU Layton|accessdate=2011-11-05|publisher=Cubed3|year=2011|author=Riley, Adam|archive-date=2013-10-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131004214139/http://www.cubed3.com/news/16056|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="getalondonlife">{{Cite web|url=http://www.ign.com/blogs/andreweisen/2011/11/14/get-a-london-life/|title=Get a London Life|accessdate=2011-11-14|publisher=IGN|year=2011|author=Eisen, Andrew|archive-date=2012-02-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120204224451/http://www.ign.com/blogs/andreweisen/2011/11/14/get-a-london-life|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 情节 ==

=== 设定 ===

《雷顿教授与魔神之笛》发生于《雷顿教授与不可思议城镇》情节的三年前，本作故事发生在一个虚构英国小镇——雾谷<ref name="l5iapr">{{cite web|url=http://level5ia.com/news/professor-layton-and-the-last-specter-is-in-stores-now/|title=Professor Layton and the Last Specter is in Stores Now!|accessdate=2011-11-05|publisher=Level-5 International America|year=2011|archive-date=2011-11-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111104170458/http://level5ia.com/news/professor-layton-and-the-last-specter-is-in-stores-now/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在雾谷的村民中流传着这样一个传说：当魔神之笛被吹响时，传说中的魔神就会从大雾中出现并保护村庄。最近，一个怪物在半夜袭击村庄并毁坏房屋建筑，而村民认为怪物正是这个魔神<ref name="l5iapr" />。

雾谷是一个被水包围的小镇，而村民也经常乘坐河道上的游船在小镇穿行<ref name="limbsofthetown">{{cite video game |title= Professor Layton and the Last Specter|developer= [[Level-5|Level-5]]|publisher= [[Nintendo|Nintendo]]|date= 2011-10-17|platform= [[Nintendo_DS|Nintendo DS]]|version= 1.0|scene= Layton's Journal|level= The Limbs of the Town|language= |isolang= |quote= The canals that wind through Misthallery are not just for show. They are also a useful means of transportation for the inhabitants, which is evident from the number of piers and small boats moored about town.}}</ref>。小镇被这些河道划分为五个区域：格兰桥、市场、东区、艾利诺斯街和海亚德岭。格兰桥包括图书馆和镇长和克拉克·特雷顿的家，市场是一个被神秘实体黑鸦控制的地方<ref name="theblackravens">{{cite video game |title= Professor Layton and the Last Specter|developer= [[Level-5|Level-5]]|publisher= [[Nintendo|Nintendo]]|date= 2011-10-17|platform= [[Nintendo_DS|Nintendo DS]]|version= 1.0|scene= Layton's Journal|level= The Black Ravens |language= |isolang= |quote= When we arrived at the auction all, the Black Raven himself was waiting for us. At first glance, it is hard to tell who or what this Black Raven is, but it is clear to me that he is simply made up of a group of children, albeit remarkably clever children. By creating this fantastical character, they were able to set their elaborate tests and select clients for the Black Market.}}</ref>，东区包括了废弃的仓库<ref name="totheoldfactory">{{cite video game |title= Professor Layton and the Last Specter|developer= [[Level-5|Level-5]]|publisher= [[Nintendo|Nintendo]]|date= 2011-10-17|platform= [[Nintendo_DS|Nintendo DS]]|version= 1.0|scene= Layton's Journal|level= To the Old Factory|language= |isolang= |quote= Thanks to the Black Ravens' help in examining the results of our trap, we now know that the specter was heading to the abandoned factory. As I recall, the factory is east of the Grand Bridge.}}</ref>，艾利诺斯街和海亚德岭则主要是住宅区。在郊区海亚德山的远离村庄的庄园里，居住着前任镇长的孩子。镇上的居民认为这里住着诅咒之女<ref name="thegirlwhowascalledawitch">{{cite video game |title= Professor Layton and the Last Specter|developer= [[Level-5|Level-5]]|publisher= [[Nintendo|Nintendo]]|date= 2011-10-17|platform= [[Nintendo_DS|Nintendo DS]]|version= 1.0|scene= Layton's Journal|level= The Girl Who Was Called a Witch|language= |isolang= |quote= Arianna, the infamous "calamity witch," turned out to be quite an ordinary little girl, although she seemed to harbor a great deal of bitterness and hostility. She is convinced that her life is cursed.}}</ref>。有传言称小镇有着隐藏的古遗迹——黄金宫<ref name="noegallery">{{Cite web|url=http://www.nintendo.co.uk/NOE/en_GB/games/ms/plsc/gallery.html|title=Professor Layton and the Spectre's Call – Gallery|accessdate=2011-11-12|publisher=Nintendo of Europe|year=2011|work=Professor Layton and the Spectre's Call – Official Website}}{{dead link|date=2018年2月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>。

=== 剧情 ===

在故事的开始，一位叫蕾米·阿尔塔瓦的女性受聘成为一所虚构大学，格雷森海拉大学教授雷顿的助手。在她自我介绍的同时，雷顿正朝着一个叫“雾谷”的小镇前进。据雷顿挚友克拉克在信中所述，有个魔神在夜里袭击村庄。然而到达克拉克的家，雷顿发现寄信人不是克拉克，而是他的儿子——能预测魔神攻击地点的路克，路克希望雷顿能帮助他们阻止魔神<ref name="noegallery" />。路克溜出了他的家，并加入了雷顿与蕾米的探索队伍。在雾谷完成了一天的探索后，他们去了当地一家旅馆过夜。而当他们听到笛子的声音向外望时，随着大雾出现了一个巨大而模糊的身影，它毁坏了镇子并开出一条道路，之后便消失的无影无踪。

翌日，为了找到传说中能召唤出幽灵的长笛——魔神之笛，雷顿、蕾米和路克三人来到了黑市。在得到由市场上孩子们扮演黑鸦团的信任后<ref name="theblackravens" />，雷顿得知长笛被已故的雾谷最大富豪阿兰巴德买走，而不久之前魔神也开始攻击城镇。三人去阿兰巴德宅看望他的女儿尤拉——曾经路克的朋友，但现在患了绝症，被市民认为是灾厄之女的人<ref name="thegirlwhowascalledawitch" />。

然而尤拉拒绝和任何人说话，因而雷顿和路克留在小镇继续询问村民，而蕾米去[[苏格兰场|苏格兰场]]去查询有关阿兰巴德死亡的档案。在警长切米尔的和克罗斯基的帮助下，蕾米记录下了情况并回到雾谷与雷顿和路克会和<ref name="foundthedocuments">{{cite video game |title= Professor Layton and the Last Specter|developer= [[Level-5|Level-5]]|publisher= [[Nintendo|Nintendo]]|date= 2011-10-17|platform= [[Nintendo_DS|Nintendo DS]]|version= 1.0|scene= Layton's Journal|level= Found the Documents!|language= |isolang= |quote= With some extra help from Inspector Chelmey, we managed to find the reports we were looking for. I also got my photographs developed, so I'm all set to go back to Misthallery. I might have accidentally picked up Inspector Grosky too...}}</ref>。警长克罗斯基希望能以自己的影响力说服雾谷镇警长杰克斯提供更多的信息，便跟随蕾米一起返回。然而警长杰克斯坚决反对调查阿兰巴德的死亡，并要求雷顿一行在24小时内离开<ref name="wegettheblame">{{cite video game |title= Professor Layton and the Last Specter|developer= [[Level-5|Level-5]]|publisher= [[Nintendo|Nintendo]]|date= 2011-10-17|platform= [[Nintendo_DS|Nintendo DS]]|version= 1.0|scene= Layton's Journal|level= We Get the Blame?|language= |isolang= |quote= We managed to witness the specter again, but as we set off after it, we were caught by Jakes and his men and forcibly taken to the police station. Does Jakes really think that we were behind all this? I very much doubt it. No, I believe there is something that Jakes doesn't want us to uncover...}}</ref>。虽然受到了杰克斯的威胁，但雷顿一行还是拜访了尤拉，并向她解释了镇中居民和她父亲关系。尤拉接受了他们，引导他们到附近湖前并吹响了魔神之笛，这时一个名为拉格西史前水生生物浮出了水面。

这时警长杰克斯出现在湖边，他称其是尾随教授而来，并要带走魔神并操作者尤拉和拉格西。 趁其不在之时，雷顿三人在镇的一个废弃的工厂内找到真正的“幽灵”<ref name="totheoldfactory" />。就在杰克斯指控尤拉和拉格西之时，雷顿出现并揭开了幽灵的真实面目：破坏镇子的事实上是为搜索镇下古遗址“黄金谷”而造的挖掘机<ref name="noegallery" />。他接着说道：杰克斯计划成为镇长，并和一个寻找黄金谷的科学家简·迪斯科尔成为同谋，而迪斯科尔则伪装成克拉克管家，并挟持其妻子和管家来做要挟<ref name="emmytotherescue">{{cite video game |title= Professor Layton and the Last Specter|developer= [[Level-5|Level-5]]|publisher= [[Nintendo|Nintendo]]|date= 2011-10-17|platform= [[Nintendo_DS|Nintendo DS]]|version= 1.0|scene= Art|level= Emmy to the Rescue|language= |isolang= |quote= Emmy helps the real Doland and Clark's wife, Brenda, escape from the cellar. What a relief to find them alive and well!}}</ref>。随着计划败露，迪斯科尔把它的机器变成一个巨大的机甲，并做寻找黄金谷的最后一次尝试。

在雷顿、路克、蕾米、拉格西和黑鸦团的协力下最终击败了机甲，而迪斯科尔也被迫逃走。尽管拉格西战斗中受了致命伤，但她继仍然续破坏镇大坝的闸门，在湖干燥后，黄金谷的人口露了出来<ref name="paradisefound">{{cite video game |title= Professor Layton and the Last Specter|developer= [[Level-5|Level-5]]|publisher= [[Nintendo|Nintendo]]|date= 2011-10-17|platform= [[Nintendo_DS|Nintendo DS]]|version= 1.0|scene= Layton's Journal|level= Paradise Found|language= |isolang= |quote= Though the struggle was over and the town saved, the badly wounded Loosha fought on to knock down the last floodgates, draining the lake of water and revealing a hidden door. When we solved the puzzle and opened the door, before us lay a paradise of lush greenery, an entire ecosystem... We had found the Golden Garden. Loosha had used the last of her strength to find a cure for Arianna.}}</ref>。在几人进入黄金谷后，拉格西死了，而尤拉也知道了她的真正目的：拉格西知道的这里干净的环境有助于治愈尤拉的疾病，而为了让尤拉有足够的时间治疗，拉格西便一直阻止着“魔神”<ref name="paradisefound" />。一年后，尤拉的病完全康复，而黄金谷的发现也公之于众，雷顿在考古学领域的名气也大增。

在黄金谷时，路克意识到世界中仍有很多他要学习等东西，并希望雷顿收其为徒，雷顿接受了他。在游戏结束时，路克告别了雾谷的居民后，便跟着雷顿开始他的旅程。

== 开发与发行 ==

=== 开发 ===

《魔神之笛》中的所有谜题都由日本教授多湖辉所作，在日销量1200万的头脑体操系列中的谜题就由他所作<ref name="noeparents">{{Cite web|url=http://www.nintendo.co.uk/NOE/en_GB/games/ms/plsc/parentsfaq.html|title=Professor Layton and the Spectre's Call – Parents FAQ|accessdate=2011-11-12|publisher=Nintendo of Europe|year=2011|work=Professor Layton and the Spectre's Call – Official Website}}{{dead link|date=2018年2月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>。游戏由Level-5总裁[[日野晃博|日野晃博]]创作，并围绕着“解谜×遇到的故事”（{{lang|ja|ナゾトキ×出会いの物語}}）的理念而设计，同时游戏讲述了雷顿如何遇到了他的学生路克<ref name="laytonjp">{{Cite web|url=http://www.layton.jp/majin/index.html|title=レイトン教授シリーズ|accessdate=2011-12-21|publisher=Level-5|language=ja|archive-date=2012-01-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120104195412/http://www.layton.jp/majin/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

在雷顿教授系列第三作《[[雷頓教授與最後的時間旅行|雷頓教授與最後的時間旅行]]》发行后，开发者便设想做一部[[前传|前传]]作品<ref name="1uplasttimetravel">{{cite web|url=http://www.1up.com/news/final-professor-layton-game-announced|title=Third (Final!) 'Professor Layton' Game Announced|accessdate=2011-11-07|publisher=1UP.com|year=2007|author=Sato, Yoshi|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131005012738/http://www.1up.com/news/final-professor-layton-game-announced|archivedate=2013-10-05}}</ref>。虽是如此，但在系列第三作的开发过程中就有玩家询问日野，这是否是“系列的真正终结”，而这正是他创作雷顿教授第二系列一切灵感的源头<ref name="1updevilsflute">{{cite web |url=http://www.1up.com/news/professor-layton-trilogy |title=Professor Layton and the New DS Trilogy |accessdate=2011-11-07 |publisher=1UP.com |year=2009 |author=Gifford, Kevin |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110629063349/http://www.1up.com/news/professor-layton-trilogy |archive-date=2011-06-29 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。2009年3月，日野晃博正式在《[[Fami通|Fami通]]》杂志公布了《雷顿教授与魔神之笛》，并称第二系列的游戏将会用更长时间来开发，以打消每作雷顿游戏变化都不大的观念<ref name="1updevilsflute" />。在第二系列中，每两部游戏发行之间都安排有动画电影，随《魔神之笛》一起上映的电影为《[[雷頓教授與永遠的歌姬|永远的歌姬]]》<ref name="1updevilsflute" /><ref name="ascome64">{{cite web |url=http://andriasang.com/come64/ |title=Level-5 Details Professor Layton Plans |accessdate=2011-11-07 |publisher=Andriasang |year=2009 |author=Gantayat, Anoop |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20130102022340/http://andriasang.com/come64/layton_plans/ |archivedate=2013-01-02 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。

=== 发行 ===

游戏最早于2009年11月在日本发行<ref name="ascome61">{{cite web |url=http://andriasang.com/come61/ |title=Level-5 Gives New Layton Game Red Carpet Premiere |accessdate=2011-11-07 |publisher=Andriasang |year=2009 |author=Gantayat, Anoop |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20130101225416/http://andriasang.com/come61/layton_red_carpet/ |archivedate=2013-01-01 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。在2010年[[E3游戏展|E3游戏展]]上，游戏没有随《最后的时间旅行》与任天堂3DS平台续作《雷顿教授与奇迹假面》一起展示<ref name="pgunwoundfuture">{{cite web|url=http://www.pocketgamer.co.uk/r/DS/Professor+Layton+and+the+Unwound+Future/news.asp?c=21485|title=E3 2010: Hands on with Professor Layton and the Unwound Future|accessdate=2011-11-07|publisher=Pocket Gamer|year=2011|author=Jordan, Jon|archive-date=2010-06-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100618023031/http://www.pocketgamer.co.uk/r/DS/Professor+Layton+and+the+Unwound+Future/news.asp?c=21485|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="pgmaskofmiracle">{{cite web|url=http://www.pocketgamer.co.uk/r/3DS/Professor+Layton+and+the+Mask+of+Miracle/news.asp?c=21501|title=E3 2010: Professor Layton and the Mask of Miracle heading to 3DS|accessdate=2011-11-07|publisher=Pocket Gamer|year=2011|author=Maxwell, Ben|archive-date=2010-06-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100620031528/http://www.pocketgamer.co.uk/r/3DS/Professor+Layton+and+the+Mask+of+Miracle/news.asp?c=21501|dead-url=no}}</ref>。美版游戏只在次年一个关于[[Nintendo_DSi_XL|Nintendo DSi XL]]采访中，由任天堂以“雷顿教授与恶魔之笛”（''Professor Layton and the Specter's Flute''）为名顺带提及<ref name="iwndsixl">{{Cite web |url=http://nintendods.com/iwata-asks-chapter.jsp?interviewId=4&volumeId=1&chapterId=5 |title=Iwata Asks: Nintendo DSi XL, Chapter 5 |accessdate=2011-11-11 |publisher=Nintendo |year=2010 |work=Nintendo DS Official Website |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/638Ae6vqg?url=http://nintendods.com/iwata-asks-chapter.jsp?interviewId=4 |archivedate=2011-11-12 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。在2011年5月，Level-5在美国申请了“雷顿教授和魔神之笛”的商标<ref name="lastspectername">{{cite web|url=http://www.nintendoworldreport.com/news/26408|title=Fourth Professor Layton Game Trademarked in North America|accessdate=2011-05-26|publisher=Nintendo World Report|year=2011|author=Neal Ronaghan|archive-date=2011-05-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110529092121/http://www.nintendoworldreport.com/news/26408|dead-url=no}}</ref>，同时游戏也在E3 2011上正式公开亮相<ref name="pglastspecter">{{cite web|url=http://www.pocketgamer.co.uk/r/DS/Professor+Layton+and+the+Last+Specter/news.asp?c=30511|title=E3 2011: Professor Layton and the Last Specter confirmed with spooky new shots and trailer|accessdate=2011-11-07|publisher=Pocket Gamer|year=2011|author=Schilling, Chris|archive-date=2011-11-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111106054512/http://www.pocketgamer.co.uk/r/DS/Professor+Layton+and+the+Last+Specter/news.asp?c=30511|dead-url=no}}</ref>。游戏于2011年末在北美和PAL区发行<ref name="eu name">{{cite web|url=http://www.officialnintendomagazine.co.uk/28396/professor-layton-4-uk-name-revealed |title=Professor Layton 4 UK name revealed |author=East, Thomas |publisher=Official Nintendo Magazine UK |accessdate=2011-06-30 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110703162906/http://www.officialnintendomagazine.co.uk/28396/professor-layton-4-uk-name-revealed/ |archivedate=2011-07-03 }}</ref><ref name="lastspectername" />。

