=== 音乐 ===

游戏音乐在日本以《雷顿教授与魔神之笛原声音乐》（{{lang|ja|レイトン教授と魔神の笛 オリジナル・サウンドトラック}}）之名发布了原声碟<ref name="semlstracklist">{{cite web|url=http://www.squareenixmusic.com/albums/p/professorlayton4.shtml|title=Professor Layton and the Devil's Flute Original Soundtrack|accessdate=2011-11-01|publisher=Square Enix Music|year=2009|archive-date=2012-04-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120410000034/http://www.squareenixmusic.com/albums/p/professorlayton4.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>。由[[安藤裕子|安藤裕子]]演唱的片尾曲《ラフマベティ -君が僕にくれたもの-》<ref name="ascome61" />没有收录于原声碟，代之的是国际版游戏中使用的乐器版音乐<ref name="semlstracklist" /><ref name="vgmdbpax">{{cite web|url=http://vgmdb.net/album/16129|title=Paxmáveiti -Kimi ga Boku ni Kuretamono- (Limited Edition)|accessdate=2011-11-01|publisher=VGMdb|year=2009|archive-date=2012-09-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120927095705/http://vgmdb.net/album/16129|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref name="lsmanualp26">{{cite manual | title = Professor Layton and the Last Specter Instruction Booklet| section = Professor Layton and the Last Specter Staff Credits| publisher = Nintendo of America| date = 2011-10-17| accessdate =2011-11-01 | quote = Ending Theme Music – Paxmaveiti (Lafumabety) -Kimiga Bokuni Kuretamono-; Composer: Yuko Ando, Bass: Hajime Niwa, Drums: Mikio Yamabe, Guitar: Teiji Taguchi, Piano: Shoko Tsukioka, Violin/Viola: Tatsunobu Goto|page = 26}}</ref>。游戏还重新使用了《恶魔之箱》和《最后的时间旅行》中的音乐。

游戏的配乐受到了很高的评价。史克威尔艾尼克斯给游戏原声打了8/10分<ref name="semlsreview">{{cite web|url=http://www.squareenixmusic.com/reviews/mactear/professorlayton4.shtml|title=Professor Layton and the Devil's Flute Original Soundtrack :: Review|accessdate=2011-11-01|publisher=Square Enix Music|year=2009|archive-date=2012-04-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120410194436/http://www.squareenixmusic.com/reviews/mactear/professorlayton4.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>并称其“相对于前作音乐更进了一小步”，同时评论还称赞其管弦演奏质量“更胜于已有奇妙安排的《雷顿教授与最后的时间旅行》”<ref name="semlsreview" />。RPGfan同样赞扬了游戏的管弦乐，并也给给了其余配乐高度评价，评论尤为称赞“魔神之笛主题乐”，称其“必能赢得所有电子游戏音乐迷的心”。

